OL,5, A hedgehog died after being spotted    
OL,6, engulfed in a "ball of flames" after   
OL,7, being set on fire.                     
OL,9,FA passer-by tried to save the animal as
OL,10,Fit was attacked in a park in Aberdare, 
OL,11,FRhondda Cynon Taf, between 17:00 and   
OL,12,F18:00 BST on Thursday.                 
OL,14,FThey gave first aid but a decision was 
OL,15,Flater taken to put the creature down,  
OL,16,Faccording to Hedgehog Helpline.        
OL,18,FSouth Wales Police has appealed for    
OL,19,Fanyone who may have "seen a group of   
OL,20,Fyouths acting suspiciously".           
